Step  1:- Download and Install My sql server workbench
Step  2:- Setup the application and set the password for sql workbench
Step  3:- Create database and Create table in that database
Step 4:- it is maven project to go to pom.xml and Dependencies
<dependency>
    <groupId>mysql</groupId>
    <artifactId>mysql-connector-java</artifactId>
    <version>8.0.33</version>
</dependency>
Step 5:- Go to Maven tab and reload all the dependencies
and click on sync
Step 6:-connect Application to database
